      <p>A <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Bullet_graph">bullet graph</a> is a variation of a bar graph developed by Stephen Few.
      Seemingly inspired by the traditional thermometer charts and progress bars found in many dashboards,
      the bullet graph serves as a replacement for dashboard gauges and meters.</p>
      
      <p>This example is a simplification of the excellent Protovis Bullet Graph component originally written by Clint Ivy and Jamie Love.</p>
      
